   [redball.gif] NEdit

  A GUI style plain-text editor for X/Motif systems

   [redball.gif] Histo-Scope

  A tool to select and display histograms, n-tuples, and scalar values from a
  program as data is being created or analyzed

   [redball.gif] NPlot

  A tool for quickly plotting columnar data from text files

   [redball.gif] Histo-Scope Plotting Widgets

  A collection of six Motif widgets for graphing and plotting

   [redball.gif] NFit

  The Nirvana Graphical User Interface to MINUIT

   [redball.gif] Java Explorations

  Exploring Java3D for display of 2D Histograms
